flowchart LR
    Client([Client]) -->|HTTPS| LB{{Load Balancer}}
    LB --> Gateway

    subgraph backend [Backend Service]
        direction TB
        Gateway[API Gateway] --> AuthZ{Authorized?}
        AuthZ -->|no| Deny[/401 Unauthorized/]
